data.description: Check out this 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home on a spacious quarter acre lot in a desirable location. This 1513 square foot home boasts recently remodeled bathrooms and an open floor plan perfect for entertaining. The large backyard has views of Mount Garfield and features RV parking and a patio area.  Updates were just completed in October 2022 including brand new flooring, light fixtures, and countertops in both bathrooms. The kitchen features a gas range and an large dining area. All three bedrooms are nicely sized with ample closet space. Priced to sell at only $350,000, this home is a rare find and won't last long.
